data.description: Discover your dream home on a private, dead-end road in coveted Westwood. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem offers vaulted ceilings and abundant natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere. Enjoy a spacious layout with the potential for Dual Living or In-Law quarters. The property features a delightful, manicured yard with lush greenery and a covered patio for seamless indoor-outdoor entertaining. This home is equipped with energy-saving solar panels, bringing you roughly $13 in monthly electricity costs. The kitchen showcases granite counters and stainless-steel appliances. The fresh carpet and paint throughout revitalize the interior, breathing new life into every room and providing a blank canvas for your personal touch. Welcome to your next chapter!
